    "result": {"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"dopoto"}},"markdownRemark":{"id":"a1e28d02-9367-52e7-be88-eb39fbec6e78","excerpt":"I was running a Karma test suite containing a few hundred unit tests, when I got into this error: Now, I happen to know that this is caused by a missing [NO…","html":"<p>I was running a Karma test suite containing a few hundred unit tests, when I got into this error:</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"js\"><pre class=\"language-js\"><code class=\"language-js\">Can’t bind to ‘some<span class=\"token operator\">-</span>property’ since it isn’t a \nknown property <span class=\"token keyword\">of</span> ‘some<span class=\"token operator\">-</span>component’</code></pre></div>\n<p>Now, I happen to know that this is caused by a missing [NO_ERRORS_SCHEMA] in one or more of the spec files.</p>\n<p>But — the Karma tests runner does not provide any info about the actual names of the files having this issue.</p>\n<p>So — how to solve this problem then: “get a list of all *.spec.ts files in my project that do not contain the ‘NO_ERRORS_SCHEMA’ string”?</p>\n<p>Luckily, there’s a Visual Studio Code extension for that:\n<a href=\"https://marketplace.visualstudio.com/items?itemName=DanishSarwar.reverse-search\">ReverseSearch</a>.\nOnce installed, do this:</p>\n<ol>\n<li>Press Ctrl + P, open Reverse Search:</li>\n</ol>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 625px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/63e472b81b58586a5b258394d22b47b0/80d71/1.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 14.556962025316455%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAABQAAAADCAIAAAAcOLh5AAAACXBIWXMAAA7CAAAOwgEVKEqAAAAAg0lEQVQI14XKTQ6CMBBAYe5/MaNBWuz0T6YMQqeCrdYjGKJ7k7f4Fq+J1D5YlQSZ/6YKQ0k6J50ZmNrGjTYkQ6tbnsNcBn6HWEOsGCvyF6+fuQbaHPI+m0net7XRFsB3euiUO3WXgw1CX1sbpKfejcLg2aAwuA+eelzAk8RZSXOcbuMHTQab33qKPdAAAAAASUVORK5CYII='); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"1\"\n        title=\"1\"\n        src=\"/static/63e472b81b58586a5b258394d22b47b0/80d71/1.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/63e472b81b58586a5b258394d22b47b0/c26ae/1.png 158w,\n/static/63e472b81b58586a5b258394d22b47b0/6bdcf/1.png 315w,\n/static/63e472b81b58586a5b258394d22b47b0/80d71/1.png 625w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 625px) 100vw, 625px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<ol start=\"2\">\n<li>Enter a string. We’ll use “NO_ERRORS_SCHEMA” here:</li>\n</ol>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 614px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/d8351dce80589a5e2aa915a14f281295/e9131/2.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 12.025316455696203%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAABQAAAACCAIAAADXZGvcAAAACXBIWXMAAA7CAAAOwgEVKEqAAAAAPklEQVQI143GQQqAQAwEwf3/P53MJJiNWb2LePUgFE2P8K2mZ2qtvM75X+4cHgGAEswAGPlEet/I7j6+VNUNuElv1wLGhL8AAAAASUVORK5CYII='); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"2\"\n        title=\"2\"\n        src=\"/static/d8351dce80589a5e2aa915a14f281295/e9131/2.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/d8351dce80589a5e2aa915a14f281295/c26ae/2.png 158w,\n/static/d8351dce80589a5e2aa915a14f281295/6bdcf/2.png 315w,\n/static/d8351dce80589a5e2aa915a14f281295/e9131/2.png 614w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 614px) 100vw, 614px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<ol start=\"3\">\n<li>Choose files to include. We’ll use ”**/*.component.spec.ts” here:</li>\n</ol>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 618px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/948a472026a69da3c9a44a5ec75c714d/6e6fb/3.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 12.658227848101264%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAABQAAAADCAIAAAAcOLh5AAAACXBIWXMAAA7CAAAOwgEVKEqAAAAAYUlEQVQI133IywqAIBCFYd//ZbJXqZa1cMZaaeh4KwyKobYGH5yfI+ZBzkP3GSXjlsvUs/GPcBR9SLsLzkcKmWL2lCjkfNRy1HLWet0tAhG2VQMojaAROHjU+yAoY41teABn4Z/MdU6BxQAAAABJRU5ErkJggg=='); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"3\"\n        title=\"3\"\n        src=\"/static/948a472026a69da3c9a44a5ec75c714d/6e6fb/3.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/948a472026a69da3c9a44a5ec75c714d/c26ae/3.png 158w,\n/static/948a472026a69da3c9a44a5ec75c714d/6bdcf/3.png 315w,\n/static/948a472026a69da3c9a44a5ec75c714d/6e6fb/3.png 618w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 618px) 100vw, 618px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<ol start=\"4\">\n<li>Choose files to exclude. We’ll use ”!**/*.component.spec.ts” here:</li>\n</ol>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 613px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/ac85d11565f16b4d041b00c392c20855/5754a/4.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 11.39240506329114%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAABQAAAACCAIAAADXZGvcAAAACXBIWXMAAA7CAAAOwgEVKEqAAAAARklEQVQI13XHQQqAMAwEQP//TSG72zZJa/oAQY8izGWO3s4M+rBXBjMYDh82k7v8j7sdrXcAUgMJkBJAqdkTSlX7qvqaa91yQ29G9DFwzAAAAABJRU5ErkJggg=='); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"4\"\n        title=\"4\"\n        src=\"/static/ac85d11565f16b4d041b00c392c20855/5754a/4.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/ac85d11565f16b4d041b00c392c20855/c26ae/4.png 158w,\n/static/ac85d11565f16b4d041b00c392c20855/6bdcf/4.png 315w,\n/static/ac85d11565f16b4d041b00c392c20855/5754a/4.png 613w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 613px) 100vw, 613px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<ol start=\"5\">\n<li>Done! Matching files will be presented in the Output panel:</li>\n</ol>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 613px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/e9a716cf2fa1109c7f42d7579f7ede64/5754a/5.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 21.51898734177215%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"5\"\n        title=\"5\"\n        src=\"/static/e9a716cf2fa1109c7f42d7579f7ede64/5754a/5.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/e9a716cf2fa1109c7f42d7579f7ede64/c26ae/5.png 158w,\n/static/e9a716cf2fa1109c7f42d7579f7ede64/6bdcf/5.png 315w,\n/static/e9a716cf2fa1109c7f42d7579f7ede64/5754a/5.png 613w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 613px) 100vw, 613px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>Cool, right?</p>","frontmatter":{"title":"Visual Studio Code — finding all files that *do not* contain a certain string","date":"December 04, 2021","description":"Visual Studio Code — finding all files that *do not* contain a certain string"}},"previous":{"fields":{"slug":"/2021111-remote-beep-demo-net-6-signalr-angular-13-ngrx copy/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"RemoteBeep — a demo using .NET 6, SignalR, Angular 13 and NGRX"}},"next":null},"pageContext":{"id":"a1e28d02-9367-52e7-be88-eb39fbec6e78","previousPostId":"3014ce33-f496-5e96-ae62-d04c2ce67061","nextPostId":null}},
